Any value held for a long time is called "direct current", or "DC" for short. You can't hear DC, and speakers can't reproduce it.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=9">tepples</a> — Thu Oct 01, 2009 4:55 pm</p><hr />
